definitions.definition: Nothing ; something which does not exist .
A thing or person of no worth or value ; nil .
Not any quantity of number ; zero ; the score of no points in a game.
examples: 0 .335 cm is nought /zero point three three five of a centimeter.

definitions.definition: The figure or character representing, or having the shape of, zero .
